{"type": "article", "id": 19475, "title": "4 根座椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-22T07:40:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122351zHXCBnVe7GkAfJgE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套座椅可以叠放成一把椅子的形状，然后从中抽拉出 4 根形状各不相同的椅子，非常巧妙。从大到小排列，最后是一个小方凳，能适合不同的体型，有一个家庭的感觉。椅子是用胶合板切割而成的，再喷上了枫叶色的条纹，然而每把椅子的花纹都有不同，上面有绿、红、橙、黄四种颜色的线条，仿佛座椅也有了自己的性格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145943Oy3RPDxQdWqoItr9.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261459449qAdDWk3cys1BFTG.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145945m7chFk6ZEXynvASb.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1227\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145945aEwlmi3pD9qxdrjQ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1235\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50977995\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145946tPaxMHC7E04ohrpn.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}